# Quality Validation Automation Script

**Purpose:** Automated validation of Four-Layer Rules System content quality with scoring and improvement suggestions

**Usage:**
```bash
# Run full quality validation
python quality_validation.py --comprehensive

# Run specific layer validation
python quality_validation.py --layer workflows

# Run real-time validation on file changes
python quality_validation.py --watch --file path/to/file.mdc

# Generate quality report
python quality_validation.py --report --output quality_report_2025-09-22.json
```

